description: The man was trying to walk from France to Spain to buy cheap cigarettes, reports say.
title: Coronavirus: Man rescued from Pyrenees fined for lockdown breach
title_page: Coronavirus: Man rescued from Pyrenees fined for lockdown breach - BBC News
maintext: However, the man fell into a stream and brambles and got lost before contacting rescuers, the service said. It said he was found quickly and airlifted to a security facility back in Perpignan.
